trans-unit.source: To upload your sms and mms please use our app.
trans-unit.target: To upload your sms and mms please use our app.

trans-unit.source: After downloading and installing app, login to your account and press "SYNC SMS" button
trans-unit.target: After downloading and installing app, login to your account and press "Sync SMS" button

trans-unit.source: To upload your messenger messages please go to messenger page and follow the instructions.
trans-unit.target: To upload your messenger messages please go to messenger page and follow the instructions.

trans-unit.source: Name can be maximum 256 characters long.
trans-unit.note: Shown when name is too long
trans-unit.target: Name can be maximum 256 characters long.

trans-unit.source: You must select at least 2 contacts.
trans-unit.note: Shown when not enough contacts are selected
trans-unit.target: You must select at least 2 contacts.

trans-unit.source: You can't search without providing "Search for" or providing "from" / "to" date or setting "has Attachment"
trans-unit.target: You can't search without providing "Search for" or providing "from" / "to" date or setting "has Attachment"

trans-unit.source: Facebook name can be maximum 256 characters long.
trans-unit.note: Shown when facebook name is too long
trans-unit.target: Facebook name can be maximum 256 characters long.

trans-unit.source: You must select file to import.
trans-unit.target: You must select file to import.

trans-unit.source: Error - No messages in imported file
trans-unit.target: Error - No messages in imported file

trans-unit.source: Go to Settings & Privacy > Settings > Your Facebook information > Download your data.
trans-unit.target: Go to Settings & Privacy > Settings > Your Facebook information > Download your data.

trans-unit.source: Select range, format JSON and media quality. In your information section select Messages.
trans-unit.target: Select range, format JSON and media quality. In your information section select Messages.

trans-unit.source: Wait until file is generated (may took a long time).
trans-unit.target: Wait until file is generated (may took a long time).

trans-unit.source: If there was more than one file please merge them into one .zip file. You must unzip all files and then zip them into single zip archive. To do this you can use WinRar or 7zip. Directory messages must be in the archive root.
trans-unit.target: If there was more than one file please merge them into one .zip file. You must unzip all files and then zip them into single zip archive. To do this you can use WinRar or 7zip. Directory messages must be in the archive root.

trans-unit.source: Add previously created and downloaded file (Choose file).
trans-unit.target: Add previously created and downloaded file (Choose file).

trans-unit.source:
If there are no new messages after import please ensure that your zip file contains messages data (at least one message_1.json file). This could happen if you have no messages within selected dates or not merged zip files.
If you import many files please ensure to do it in chronological order.
trans-unit.target:
If there are no new messages after import please ensure that your zip file contains messages data (at least one message_1.json file). This could happen if you have no messages within selected dates or not merged zip files.
If you import many files please ensure to do it in chronological order.

trans-unit.target: There is file upload in progress

trans-unit.target: Username must contain a maximum of characters.
